{"tid":158352,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"腸胃唔好食尖椒真係好刺激","createTime":"2017-03-16T08:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T15:47:49.000Z","uid":91947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4416b676bea32f787d234682d2ee8580f8d632a5","tid":158352,"uid":91947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"食尖椒就好似俄羅斯輪盤咁<br />\n上一舊唔辣<br />\n下一舊可以辣到仆街<br />\n但食尖椒唧精髓就係呢種搏奕嘅心態<br />\n食完嘅刺激嘅感覺一路由食道去到胃部<br />\n經過小腸再經大腸繞過腹部一個圈去到直腸<br />\n我以為只係腸胃受刺激需釋出氣體<br />\n放是輕輕放鬆排泄口<br />\n果然一湧而出但覺得有少少異樣<br />\n點解啲氣體有溫度同重量<br />\n慢慢開始臭但唔係擴散出嚟<br />\n而係滲上嚟同開始感覺到濕<br />\n我就知今次真係瀨野<br />\n去左廁所冷靜處理<br />\n果然我冇估錯<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/160735_2730e88fb1dc2152d6d1a77a0cb2c1f0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F160735_2730e88fb1dc2152d6d1a77a0cb2c1f0.jpg&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5f36c105\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/160735_2730e88fb1dc2152d6d1a77a0cb2c1f0.jpg</a>（慎入）<br />\n於是除左條底褲丟左佢<br />\n清潔好自己就咁著返面褲就算<br />\n但係仲感覺到涼涼地<br />\n原來面褲都濕左<br />\n不過好在係黑色褲<br />\n隱約有啲味但至少睇唔出<br />\n陣間開會咁多人應該唔會有人知<br />\n不過下次最好都係唔好腸胃唔好嘅時候食尖椒"},{"pid":"dd7c8696ae13224af32f2b2c996b006f817ebea9","tid":158352,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"eb6be8955b21b77aa22ba324e4eadd78134f5c62","tid":158352,"uid":91947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渣ga</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7565e566869982850e85e5cce32ab8871052ac93","tid":158352,"uid":12941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d902ede06b44b3b940665519f5be67ac2f9a5b","tid":158352,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}